#
# Starter Colang flows for the SingleAxis Fabric nemo-sidecar.
#
# This file is intentionally empty of active flows. Jailbreak detection
# is handled by the sidecar's deterministic literal pre-filter (see
# `fabric_nemo_sidecar.literal_filter` and `config.yml`). The file is
# kept rather than deleted because `RailsConfig.from_path(...)`
# expects a Colang source file present in any rails directory.
#
# To add LLM-graded rails, append your own `define user ...` /
# `define flow ...` blocks below and reference them from `config.yml`.
